34
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:20,139
named Ye Dong.

35
00:02:21,340 --> 00:02:22,259
I can see

36
00:02:22,659 --> 00:02:23,840
something is on her mind.

37
00:02:24,539 --> 00:02:26,819
She looked distressed and sad.

38
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:29,419
She said everyone around her is a demon.

39
00:02:29,419 --> 00:02:30,919
Doesn't that mean you?

40
00:02:31,379 --> 00:02:32,479
Be honest with me.

41
00:02:33,740 --> 00:02:36,060
What outrageous things have you done?

42
