You...

43
00:02:42,580 --> 00:02:42,879
You...

44
00:02:44,219 --> 00:02:44,539
You...

45
00:02:44,539 --> 00:02:45,699
You won't say, huh?

46
00:02:45,759 --> 00:02:46,219
You brat,

47
00:02:46,379 --> 00:02:47,860
just admit it.

48
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:48,419
Mom,

49
00:02:49,259 --> 00:02:50,259
what are you doing?

50
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,819
Cheng Nuo,

51
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,620
no matter what you've done,

52
00:02:55,340 --> 00:02:56,860
be honest

53
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,539
and explain it to me.

54
00:02:59,219 --> 00:03:00,539
Make amends where it's needed,

55
00:03:01,979 --> 00:03:03,219
and make up for what's lost.

56
00:03:04,219 --> 00:03:05,139
If you are wrong,

57
00:03:05,259 --> 00:03:06,139
you must admit it.

58
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:07,580
I believe

59
00:03:08,020 --> 00:03:10,259
you're not an irredeemable person.

60
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:11,699
Mom,

61
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:13,860
please don't worry.

62
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:15,500
If I don't, who will?

63
00:03:15,939 --> 00:03:17,300
Bai Cha has no parents.

64
00:03:18,139 --> 00:03:19,900
As her mother-in-law,

65
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:22,000
I'm her guardian.

66
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:24,180
Want me to stay out of it?

67
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:26,360
Unless you stop being my son.

68
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:31,939
She got pregnant for you

69
00:03:31,939 --> 00:03:33,240
and had a miscarriage,

70
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,939
yet you betrayed her.

71
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:39,900
Last night, you didn't come home.

72
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:42,199
Are you...

73
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:46,139
You,

74
00:03:46,379 --> 00:03:46,580
you!

75
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:47,319
Mom.

76
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:48,740
You brat,

77
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:50,319
admit it.

78
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:50,639
Mom.

79
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:52,280
Admit it.

80
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,300
Admit you're wrong!

81
00:03:55,699 --> 00:03:56,180
Mom,

82
00:03:58,740 --> 00:04:00,020
I wronged Bai Cha.

83
00:04:01,180 --> 00:04:02,460
I wronged our child.

84
00:04:05,379 --> 00:04:05,979
Cheng Nuo,

85
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:08,379
no matter what you've done,

86
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:10,259
I have only one request.

87
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:11,500
Now,

88
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:13,560
make amends with her

89
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:14,939
and bring her back.

90
00:04:16,139 --> 00:04:16,660
Mom,

91
00:04:21,139 --> 00:04:21,740
Bai Cha

92
00:04:22,899 --> 00:04:24,060
will never come back.

93
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:07,139
The real Bai Cha

94
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,319
