95
00:05:11,279 --> 00:05:11,959
when she

96
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,779
fell off the cliff.

97
00:05:16,259 --> 00:05:17,379
She's dead?

98
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:19,339
Don't talk nonsense!

99
00:05:19,579 --> 00:05:20,339
That's...

100
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,040
That is

101
00:05:22,019 --> 00:05:22,899
Lin Xia.

102
00:05:23,379 --> 00:05:24,660
What Lin Xia?

103
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:26,579
How is this possible?

104
00:05:27,019 --> 00:05:27,899
But she clearly is...

105
00:05:27,899 --> 00:05:28,379
Mom.

106
00:05:29,579 --> 00:05:30,100
Mom,

107
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:31,620
listen to me.

108
00:06:14,899 --> 00:06:15,740
Lin Xia

109
00:06:16,379 --> 00:06:17,779
