110
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:20,339
She assumed Bai Cha's identity

111
00:06:21,019 --> 00:06:22,180
to start anew

112
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:24,899
and reclaim what belongs to her.

113
00:06:28,339 --> 00:06:29,860
What a pitiful girl!

114
00:06:31,740 --> 00:06:33,540
And my poor daughter-in-law,

115
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:34,220
Bai Cha.

116
00:06:35,819 --> 00:06:38,060
Both are victims of demon Ye Dong.

117
00:06:38,819 --> 00:06:39,259
Cheng Nuo.

118
00:06:40,139 --> 00:06:41,540
Let's call the police now.

119
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:43,740
Have that demon arrested.

120
00:06:44,019 --> 00:06:44,620
Mom,

121
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:46,620
I have my own plans.

122
00:06:46,660 --> 00:06:47,740
I kept it from you

123
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:50,139
for your own safety.

124
00:06:50,699 --> 00:06:51,300
Cheng Nuo.

125
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:53,420
I understand your difficulties.

126
00:06:53,699 --> 00:06:54,939
I won't interfere.

127
00:06:55,779 --> 00:06:56,100
But

128
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,980
promise me one thing.

129
00:06:58,939 --> 00:06:59,459
Tell me,

130
00:06:59,779 --> 00:07:00,139
Mom.

131
00:07:02,579 --> 00:07:04,220
Protect yourselves,

132
00:07:05,019 --> 00:07:06,740
especially Lin Xia.

133
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:09,160
She's suffered enough in this life.

134
00:07:10,899 --> 00:07:11,860
I understand.

135
00:07:25,980 --> 00:07:27,339
(From now on,)

136
00:07:27,779 --> 00:07:29,379
(you are no longer Lin Xia.)

137
00:07:30,459 --> 00:07:32,139
(You are Bai Cha.)

138
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:35,980
(All of this)

139
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,680
(is Ye Dong's fault.)

140
00:07:42,180 --> 00:07:43,120
(Ye Dong,)

141
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:45,879
(I will reclaim everything)

142
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:48,220
(I've lost.)

143
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:54,279
You saved me.

144
00:07:56,379 --> 00:07:57,540
Everyone thinks

145
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,100
Bai Cha

146
00:07:59,660 --> 00:08:00,779
was merely injured.

147
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,300
But she died
when she fell off the cliff.

148
00:08:04,779 --> 00:08:05,980
It's Ye Dong's fault.

149
00:08:07,579 --> 00:08:08,939
I imagine you hate Ye Dong

150
00:08:10,019 --> 00:08:11,139
no less than I do.

151
00:08:14,339 --> 00:08:16,699
I want him to face proper judgment.

152
00:08:17,100 --> 00:08:18,899
I'll reclaim what's rightfully mine.

153
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:23,540
I can help you,

154
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:25,540
but I have one condition.

155
00:08:27,579 --> 00:08:28,379
What is it?

156
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,720
I can help you reclaim

157
00:08:32,419 --> 00:08:33,700
everything you've lost,

158
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:35,740
but you must promise me

159
00:08:36,179 --> 00:08:37,659
to follow my plan exactly.

160
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:39,580
What plan?

161
00:08:42,899 --> 00:08:44,440
Now that your face is disfigured

162
00:08:45,379 --> 00:08:47,019
and you're wanted everywhere,

163
00:08:48,059 --> 00:08:48,860
you should

164
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:50,620
assume Bai Cha's identity

165
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,480
and return to Ye Dong.

166
00:08:55,539 --> 00:08:57,860
Have you been monitoring him all along?

167
00:08:58,220 --> 00:08:58,779
Yes.

168
00:09:00,139 --> 00:09:01,139
Then my father's death...

169
00:09:01,139 --> 00:09:01,740
Your father...

170
00:09:06,220 --> 00:09:07,179
I discovered his death

171
00:09:08,940 --> 00:09:11,220
when I tracked them dumping the body.

172
00:09:11,860 --> 00:09:12,460
At that time,

173
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:13,500
I tried to save you,

174
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:15,820
but failed.

175
00:09:17,139 --> 00:09:18,220
Lin Na's death

176
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:19,899
was also an accident.

177
00:09:22,539 --> 00:09:24,440
Why didn't you call the police earlier?

178
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:25,620
If you called the police,

179
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:26,639
Na wouldn't have died.

180
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:27,820
I considered doing so,

181
00:09:28,779 --> 00:09:29,820
but do you know

182
00:09:31,620 --> 00:09:33,500
Man City has no death penalty?

183
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,740
I want that bad guy

184
00:09:37,539 --> 00:09:38,519
to pay for his crimes

185
00:09:39,220 --> 00:09:40,220
with his life.

186
00:09:56,419 --> 00:09:57,000
Hello.

187
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,440
Why didn't you pick up earlier?

188
00:10:00,220 --> 00:10:01,259
Miss me so much

189
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:02,299
